{"id":117,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":117,"title":"D&C 113","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 113"],[".studyIntro",["i","Answers to certain questions on the writings of Isaiah, given by Joseph Smith the Prophet, at or near Far West, Missouri, March 1838."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.1-6"},"1–6"],", The Stem of Jesse, the rod coming therefrom, and the root of Jesse are identified;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.7-10"},"7–10"],", The scattered remnants of Zion have a right to the priesthood and are called to return to the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.1","order":"06.05.113.14635"},["b","1"],"Who is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Stem of Jesse"],"spoken of in the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.1-5"},"1st, 2d, 3d, 4th, and 5th verses of the 11th chapter of Isaiah"],"?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.2","order":"06.05.113.14636"},["b","2"],"Verily thus saith the Lord: It is Christ."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.3","order":"06.05.113.14637"},["b","3"],"What is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"rod"],"spoken of in the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.1"},"first verse of the 11th chapter of Isaiah"],", that should come of the Stem of Jesse?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.4","order":"06.05.113.14638"},["b","4"],"Behold, thus saith the Lord: It is a servant in the hands of Christ, who is partly a descendant of Jesse as well as of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Ephraim"],", or of the house of Joseph, on whom there is laid much",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"power"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.5","order":"06.05.113.14639"},["b","5"],"What is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"root of Jesse"],"spoken of in the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.10"},"10th verse of the 11th chapter"],"?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.6","order":"06.05.113.14640"},["b","6"],"Behold, thus saith the Lord, it is a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"descendant"],"of Jesse, as well as of Joseph, unto whom rightly belongs the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"priesthood"],", and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"keys"],"of the kingdom, for an",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"ensign"],", and for the gathering of my people in the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_6e"},"last days"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.7","order":"06.05.113.14641"},["b","7"],"Questions by Elias Higbee: What is meant by the command in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.1"},"Isaiah, 52d chapter, 1st verse"],", which saith: Put on thy strength, O Zion—and what people had Isaiah reference to?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.8","order":"06.05.113.14642"},["b","8"],"He had reference to those whom God should call in the last days, who should hold the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"power"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"priesthood"],"to bring again",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"Zion"],", and the redemption of Israel; and to put on her",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"strength"],"is to put on the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_8e"},"authority"],"of the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_8f"},"priesthood"],", which she, Zion, has a",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_8g"},"right"],"to by lineage; also to return to that power which she had lost."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.9","order":"06.05.113.14643"},["b","9"],"What are we to understand by Zion loosing herself from the bands of her neck;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.2"},"2d verse"],"?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.10","order":"06.05.113.14644"},["b","10"],"We are to understand that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"scattered"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"remnants"],"are exhorted to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"return"],"to the Lord from whence they have fallen; which if they do, the promise of the Lord is that he will speak to them, or give them revelation. See the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.6-8"},"6th, 7th, and 8th verses"],". The",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"bands"],"of her neck are the curses of God upon her, or the remnants of Israel in their scattered condition among the Gentiles."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.1a","order":"06.05.113.14645"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.1.1-5"},"Isa. 11:1 (1–5)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-davidic-descent-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Davidic Descent of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.3a","order":"06.05.113.14647"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/110.2.1-4"},"Ps. 110:2 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.4a","order":"06.05.113.14649"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/41.52.50-52"},"Gen. 41:52 (50–52)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.34.30-34"},"D&C 133:34 (30–34)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-joseph-people-of"},"TG Israel, Joseph, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.4b","order":"06.05.113.14651"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.16.11-16"},"D&C 110:16 (11–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.5a","order":"06.05.113.14653"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/21.10.10-12"},"2 Ne. 21:10 (10–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.6a","order":"06.05.113.14655"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.10"},"Isa. 11:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.6b","order":"06.05.113.14657"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-melchizedek"},"TG Priesthood, Melchizedek"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.6c","order":"06.05.113.14659"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.11"},"D&C 110:11"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.6d","order":"06.05.113.14661"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.17"},"Isa. 30:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.9"},"D&C 45:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ensign"},"TG Ensign"],"."],["div",{"id":"6e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.6e","order":"06.05.113.14663"},["b","6e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"Last Days"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.8a","order":"06.05.113.14665"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-power-of"},"TG Priesthood, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.8b","order":"06.05.113.14667"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/86.8"},"D&C 86:8"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.8c","order":"06.05.113.14669"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.8d","order":"06.05.113.14671"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.24"},"Isa. 45:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.1"},"52:1"]